===[[Pokémon Mezastar]]===
Iris, in a version based on the animated series, appeared in [[Pokémon Mezastar]]. In this game, Iris is seen using a {{p|Excadrill}}, {{p|Haxorus}}, {{p|Dragonite}}, and {{p|Hydreigon}}, with the latter Pokémon never being used by her in the animated series, although it could be a  [[List of cross-canon references|references]] to [[Iris|her]] using Hydreigon in the [[core series]] games. In the [[Double Chain set 1 (Mezastar)|first set in the Double Chain series]], Iris also appeared as an opponent in an event that recreated the [[Masters Eight Tournament]] that ran from October 27 to November 21, 2022. Upon beating the character, the player can receive a Support Pokémon Ticket based on [[Iris's Haxorus]], with a tag partner based on [[Iris's Dragonite]].<ref>https://pokemonmezastar.com/event/e2210142/</ref>
